<D>__{completely. he didn't remember me.}
<C>__{anne}
<D>__{but, you knew he was on the train! wasn't that enough to prove you were on it, too?}
<C>__{guy}
<D>__{apparently not at the right time. they suggested i could have caught the train at baltimore after miriam was murdered. they had it all worked out }
<P>__{(taps his head)}
<D>__{in their timetables.}
<C>__{anne}
<P>__{(growing indignant}
<D>__{and increasingly}
