<C>__{guy}
<P>__{(wryly)}
<D>__{whatever it is, the police will know it. they gave me a present come take a look.}
<A>__{he crosses to the window, lifts the curtain slightly, then turns back to the others.}
<C>__{guy}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{my guardian angel.}
<A>__{the group move to look out the window, the senator with reluctance.}
<B>__{long shot exterior street from their viewpoint}
<A>__{through the window we see the figure of a man across the street. he is lighting a cigarette and strolling up and down.}
<B>__{back to group}
